      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are people, but they don't get it. they talk about \"moving on\" or \"finding new purpose\" like it's that simple. but how can you have a purpose when the person who made sense of everything is just... gone? it feels like half of my actual soul was taken. i'm just a fragment of a person now. it feels wrong to even keep pretending to be whole.",
